 nanotechnology, and analytical solutions, as well as connectors and switches. In addition, it engages in the material handling rental business; and provision of on-site testing, technical training installation, erection, commissioning, calibration, annual maintenance contract, maintenance, and support services. The company was formerly known as Jost's Fan Supply and Engineering Company Limited and changed its name to Jost's Engineering Company Limited in 1913. Jost's Engineering Company Limited was incorporated in 1907 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India."}}